genre=input('Enter Genre :').capitalize()

    s=i.split('::')
    if(year==s[1][-5:-1] or genre in s[2]):
        print(i)

year=input('Enter Year : ')
genre=input('Enter Genre :').capitalize()
for i in movie:
    s=i.split('::')
    if year:
        if year==s[1][-5:-1] and genre in s[2]:
            print(i)
    else:
        if genre in s[2]:
            print(i)
